<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Upcoming Event Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; } h1 { color: #333; } p { color: #555;
      } ul { list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Upcoming Event Notification</h1>

    <p>Dear {{username}},</p>

    <p>We wanted to remind you about the upcoming event, "{{eventName}}", which will start in 1 hour. We hope
      you are excited to attend!</p>

    <p>Event Details:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Event Name:</strong> {{eventName}}</li>
      <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</li>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{eventLocation}}</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Don't miss out! We look forward to seeing you there.</p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Eventopia Team</p>
  </body>
</html>